title: Narrative

Verifies that the unmodified <<.def "tabs">> macro auto-delegates to `<<.def "static-tabs">>` when `tv-config-static` is `yes` (the same hook used by static-render templates). No source change to the calling tiddler is required.

+
title: Output

;Auto-replacement under tv-config-static

<$let tv-config-static="yes">
<<tabs "[[SampleTabOne]] [[SampleTabTwo]] [[SampleTabThree]] [[SampleTabFour]]" "SampleTabOne" "$:/state/test/static-tabs/auto">>
</$let>
